","tid":2145670,"uid":61745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:45:13.000Z","msg":"所以呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e3e07e17815431f03d0d37f67f8e6249c884c8","tid":2145670,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"敦促美方加強接觸和對話溝通<br />\n<br />\n美帝卑劣無恥更加冇理由要求祖國同美帝對話溝通<br />\n你幾時見政府會同流氓溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即時反制才是解決之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0c4e378808357f80b07db5d388b31ec0627172","tid":2145670,"uid":177552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdkQDci.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdkQDci.gif&h=7127bb23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edcb8e4e439349aef65ab8716e69f6f996be44bb","tid":2145670,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"行文style 已經同北韓睇齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87fe68438d781bf47580674dee899cd148291c3","tid":2145670,"uid":319554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"每次都見到佢講話乜野 不可分離既一部分就覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd765ab00310b0dcb9ed2a2e2e079bd0c5f19f","tid":2145670,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd9c82a2c15c8a33ea5b6bfdfc56f892cbcfae8c","tid":2145670,"uid":273703,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces